Progressive Overview





Since 1937, drivers have trusted Progressive for their car insurance.
Fast. Fair. Better. That's what customers can expect from Progressive Direct. Everything we do acknowledges the needs of busy customers who are cost-conscious and increasingly savvy about auto insurance and good service.
We're here for you 24/7, online and by phone. We can provide quotes, update your policy, even answer "what if" questions if that's what you need. From auto quotes in about 6 minutes to our superior claims service, we find new ways to show you that we respect your time.
Here's an overview of Progressive, from the types of insurance we offer to the awards we've received. See why people choose us for their insurance needs.

