  Glenn M. Renwick – Chief Executive Officer and President of Progressive Corporation – Email Address


























































 
 

 


































Executive Email Address Directory

 





 






 

 










					Glenn M. Renwick – Chief Executive Officer and President of Progressive Corporation – Email Address	

HomeExecutivesGlenn M. Renwick – Chief Executive Officer and President of Progressive Corporation – Email Address 












Glenn M. Renwick has been the Chief Executive Officer and President at Progressive Corp. since January 2001. Mr. Renwick serves as the Chairman of the Board, Chief Executive Officer and President at Progressive Insurance Company Ltd. He serves as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President of Progressive Casualty Insurance Company. His responsibilities are to establish and uphold Progressive's Vision, Core Values, financial objectives and strategies and to assist corporate leaders in strategic planning and communication. He served as the Chief Technology Officer of Progressive Casualty Insurance Company since March 2000. He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Insurance Operations and Business Technology Process Leader at Progressive Corp. from 1998 to 2000 and also served as its Chief Information Officer from January 1998 to March 2000. He led Progressive's Consumer Marketing group and before he served as the President of various divisions within Progressive. He joined Progressive in 1986 as Auto Product Manager for Florida. He has more than 25 years in the insurance industry. Mr. Renwick has been the Chairman at Progressive Corp. since November 2013 and has been its Director since 1999. He serves as a Director of Progressive Casualty Insurance Company and The Cleveland Play House. He has been an Independent Director at UnitedHealth Group Incorporated since June 2008. He has been an Independent Director of Fiserv Inc. since November 2001. He serves as a Member of the Advisory Board of PreEmptive Solutions, LLC. He holds an Undergraduate Degree in Mathematics and Economics from the University of Canterbury, Christchurch, New Zealand and a Master's Degree in Engineering from the University of Florida, Gainesville.




The Progressive Corporation is one of the largest providers of car insurance in the United States. The company also insures motorcycles, boats, RVs and commercial vehicles, and provides home insurance through select companies. Progressive has expanded internationally as well, offering car insurance in Australia. The company was co-founded in 1937 by Jack Green and Joseph M. Lewis, and is headquartered in Mayfield Village, Ohio.[1]












 






